    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crankshaft to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain is anchored by a Variable M Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. This example is in pristine mechanical order; both rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively with full documentation. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefitting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a factory-spec multi-link rear suspension. With an immaculate original finish and a cabin free of bolster wear, this M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
