      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines showroom perfection. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original deep-gloss factory finish without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or imperfection. The interior remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple, showing zero signs of wear on the bolsters, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and feature functions with surgical precision, exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by authorized master technicians. It has been driven sparingly and with extreme care, ensuring the powertrain remains as smooth and responsive as ever. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule specimen for the most discerning enthusiast. The sale includes all original keys, the complete owner's manual set, and a detailed folder of every maintenance record from day one.",
